data.description: Location, Location, Location!!! Beautiful home extremely well maintained by the owner, the neighborhood is convenience located near schools, shopping, restaurant and Downtown of Sugar Hill. Easy access to HWY 20, I85 and 985, minutes from Mall of Georgia, home in a Cul-de-sac with private fenced backyard. This property offers a beautiful backsplash in kitchen with spectacular granite counter tops, title floors on bathrooms and hardwood floor on the entire main level, a nice laundry room with cabinets for good storage, New interior paint. This is a MUST See, will not last long!
